A cyberpunk-style illustration of a teenage figure with multiple translucent arms emerging from their body, each arm simultaneously manipulating different glowing holographic data streams and floating crystalline orbs in a neon-lit digital void. The figure stands confidently in the center, their silhouette fragmented into parallel ghostly versions of themselves, representing concurrent processes. Around them, luminous queue lines snake through the air like electric serpents, some orderly and some chaotic, connecting floating geometric nodes that pulse with cyan and magenta energy. The background features a dark matrix of interconnected circuits and pathways dissolving into abstract digital noise. The atmosphere is electric and dynamic, conveying controlled chaos and parallel execution, with reflective wet surfaces below catching the neon glow.
